```java
apply plugin: CustomPlugin

class CustomPlugin implements Plugin<Project> {
  void apply(Project project) {
    project.task('task1') << {
      println "Sample task1 in custom plugin"

    }
    project.task('task2') << {
      println "Sample task2 in custom plugin"

    }    
  }
}
task2.dependsOn task1
```

